    "description": "欢迎来到花予的世界，花语的力量将在这里凝结成魔法改变人们的思想和心灵。作为香水店店主，你用你奇妙能力种植了各种各样的魔法花朵，并创造出充满神奇魔力的香水。<br><br>不过，创造出美妙的魔法香水的秘诀不仅仅是提取花香。你需要倾听顾客的愿望，将愿望与花语相联，了解花语的深刻意义。每一朵花都有其独特的象征意义，就看你将如何挖掘顾客内心的渴望，创造出能与他们灵魂产生共鸣的香水了。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/f70ec64eb5a7ee663cac28bf42d69589.avif?t=1689013621\" width=500 height=70 /></span><br>-  了解一群拥有独特故事的角色！<br><br>- 为你的顾客调制改变灵魂和命运的香水！<br><br>- 使用各种各样的花语注入魔法来创造你的招牌香水！<br><br>- 根据你的调香和选择，迎来多种结局！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/e4fa6b25bfd1cca449b8507939bce0c5.avif?t=1689013621\" width=500 height=70 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/4c62f08ba8b30c757f27362208d18d75.avif?t=1689013621\" width=320 height=180 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/1571ed4527f1ea7b9f05583d07908532.avif?t=1689013621\" width=320 height=180 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/03ec4209f8a19d841f09bcde3efd1397.avif?t=1689013621\" width=500 height=70 /></span><br>[b在这里认识我们的常客! 马克、弗洛拉、阿兰和未夏!<br>[/b]<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2358880/extras/7b85029c8777eef37e5b93c5682fccc7.avif?t=1689013621\" width=560 height=315 /></span><br><br><br><br><br>花予的世界正等待着你去探索它的秘密，创造出能触动顾客们灵魂的香水。你准备好释放花语的力量，创造出改变世界的香味了吗？",
